    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雫が倒れた日の午後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか雫が熱を出して倒れるとはな……\n様子を見に来てみたが、きっと部屋で安静にして……",
      "startTime": 6.5089402596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……お疲れ様……",
      "startTime": 10.5333334923,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 10.5333334923
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お疲れ……って、どうして起きてるんだ！？\n寝てなきゃダメじゃないか",
      "startTime": 17.7370439938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……体調は良くなった……\nもう平気だから安心して……くちゅん",
      "startTime": 23.5990674873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "今のは誰かが私の噂をしてただけ……\nもうなんともないから大丈……くちゅん、くちゅん",
      "startTime": 31.1330509346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ごまかし切れてないぞ\nどうして平気なフリなんてするんだ",
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "だって、もうすぐオーディションなのに……\n風邪を引いたから棄権なんて……嫌だから……",
      "startTime": 45.2428632977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だからって無理をして体を壊したら元も子もないだろ\n今はしっかり休んで、風邪を治すことに専念するんだ",
      "startTime": 53.7364729405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日は……寮には誰もいないから……\n料理とか、全部……私がやらないと……",
      "startTime": 61.7917282557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "食事なら俺がいろいろ買って来たから\nほら、どれでも好きなものを食べてくれ",
      "startTime": 68.3999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "これは……レトルトのおかゆに雑炊、スープ……\n野菜ジュース、スポーツドリンク……",
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "フルーツゼリー……プリン……アイス……\nバナナに、みかんに……桃の缶詰……",
      "startTime": 85.8397100078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、買い過ぎ……",
      "startTime": 89.9999990146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな……\n雫が倒れて、俺も気が動転していたみたいだ",
      "startTime": 95.3588572703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私のことが心配で……？",
      "startTime": 99.5666656812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、こんなに一人じゃ食べ切れないから……\n一緒に食べてくれる……？",
      "startTime": 106.6999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、二人で食べようか。それで食べ終わったら\nちゃんと温かくして寝るんだぞ、いいな？",
      "startTime": 112.8428699604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "うん……分かった……",
      "startTime": 116.49999698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――食事が終わって",
      "startTime": 119.1186137755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "顔色も良くなってきたが、風邪は治りかけが肝心だ\n今日はゆっくり寝て安静にすること、いいな？",
      "startTime": 126.7333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……お母さんみたい……\nそんなに私のこと、心配……？",
      "startTime": 134.0667604389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "心配に決まってるだろ\n風邪を治して、早く元気になってくれ",
      "startTime": 139.117097512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった……言われた通りにする……\nしっかり寝て……風邪を治す……",
      "startTime": 149.0255275294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "眠そうだな……。ちゃんとベッドに入ったか？\nじゃあ、俺は仕事に戻るから……",
      "startTime": 157.1849060058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n帰っちゃう前に……言わせてほしい……",
      "startTime": 163.2333260854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "今日はみんな仕事で……寮には私一人しかいなくて……\n本当は、心細かった……",
      "startTime": 173.5695126321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "体がだるくて、頭がぼーっとして、一人は寂しくて……\nだから、お見舞いに来てくれて……嬉しかった……",
      "startTime": 185.0726657987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "……私、早く風邪を治すね……",
      "startTime": 190.6999852817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "元気になって、{user}さんと……\nまた一緒に、お仕事したいから……",
      "startTime": 199.4333242814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "……すー、すー……",
      "startTime": 205.1666560173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "眠ったか……。雫……急に倒れて俺も心配したんだぞ\n早くまた元気な顔を見せてくれ",
      "startTime": 220.5097027745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
